    <name>balistica</name>
    <summary>External ballistics software</summary>
    <description>
        <p>
        balística is a basic ballistics calculator for the Gnome Desktop Environment. It
        provides the ability to calculate the standard drag functions (G1-G8) along with
        other minor ballistics related calculations like the Greenhill Formula and the 
        Miller Twist Rule.
        </p>
        <p>balística’s features include:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Calculate a round's drag using the G1-G8 drag models</li>
            <li>Compute a bullet's twist rate using Greenhill or Miller</li>
            <li>Compute a round's Point Blank Range (PBR)</li>
        </ul>
    </description>
    <url type="homepage">http://fusliero.github.io/balistica/</url>
